text: Guy de Valle Flor (born 19 May 1920) is a Portuguese former sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Portuguese male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Portugal Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Pau, Pyrénées-Atlantiques
